ass=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">myFunction</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* Get the text field */</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> copyText <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"myInput\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* Select the text field */</span>\n            copyText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">select</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n            copyText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">setSelectionRange</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">99999</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">/* For mobile devices */</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* Copy the text inside the text field */</span>\n            navigator<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>clipboard<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">writeText</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>copyText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n            <span class=\"token comment\">/* Alert the copied text */</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"Copied the text: \"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> copyText<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>value<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    </span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- Option 1: Bootstrap Bundle with Popper --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">src</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">integrity</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>sha384-MrcW6ZMFYlzcLA8Nl+NtUVF0sA7MsXsP1UyJoMp4YLEuNSfAP+JcXn/tWtIaxVXM<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">crossorigin</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>anonymous<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token script\"></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>body</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>html</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span></code></pre></div>\n<p>Check the output of the above code example.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/3c0e0/clipboard.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50.632911392405056%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Bootstrap, Input, Clipboard\"\n        title=\"Bootstrap, Input, Clipboard\"\n        src=\"/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/828fb/clipboard.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/ff44c/clipboard.jpg 158w,\n/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/a6688/clipboard.jpg 315w,\n/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/828fb/clipboard.jpg 630w,\n/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/0ede0/clipboard.jpg 945w,\n/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/3ac88/clipboard.jpg 1260w,\n/static/65277787bb6fe93fc3dc6298e5a33e01/3c0e0/clipboard.jpg 1361w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n   